data.description: Welcome home to this charming ranch-style home nestled in the heart of Wellington. This 3 bedroom home offers an open-concept kitchen, complete with a large addition that provides valuable extra living or recreational space. House is ready for updates and some TLC.  Located with easy access to schools and abundant outdoor recreation, this home boasts all the advantages of small-town living! You'll appreciate the convenience of off-street parking, a fully fenced yard for added privacy, and no HOA or covenants, granting you total freedom. Don't let this opportunity to experience the true essence of small-town living pass you by. Located just a stone's throw away from Old Town Wellington, you'll have quick access to the town's charming restaurants and breweries, making it easy to enjoy the local flavors. Schedule your showing today!
